Importance:
Simple language and very efficient to use.
Structured program.
Easy to detect errors.

structure of c:
1.Documemtation section.
2.link section.
3.Global declaration.
4.Fuction prototype declaration.
5.Main section:
   1.Declaration part
   2.Excutive part
6.Userdefine functions.

Note: Link section and main section is mandatory.
